      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VISTA YTTRIUM (1) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and three placings from six starts. Missed the frame latest (25.68) when seventh over 431m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks a key chance on best form. ARMATREE VIOLET (2) could manage only a 3.5 lengths fifth last start over 431m at this track but in a useful 24.92. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. ROSACKY RAYO (4) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 19.62 beating RED ROCK RATTLER. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Will go close again if runs up to latest. JOCK (3) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
